    "title": "Yoeli 1:1–20:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "29001001-29001020",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Watu wa <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108480\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">ufalme wa kusini</span> walikuwa na huzuni sana. <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108199\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">Mungu</span> alikuwa ametuma janga la nzige katika nchi yao.</p><p>Hii ilikuwa kama janga la nzige ambayo Mungu alituma <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108251\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">Misri</span>. Hiyo ilikuwa wakati wa <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108308\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">tauni kumi</span>. Katika wakati wa Yoeli, nzige waliharibu mazao yote ya ufalme wa kusini.</p><p>Joel alielezea tukio hili kama <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108571\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">siku ya Bwana</span>. Hii ilimaanisha kwamba Mungu alikuwa ameleta <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108233\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">hukumu</span> dhidi ya watu wake (<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108199\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">watu wa Mungu</span>).</p><p>Joel aliwasihi watu wa Mungu kulia, kufunga chakula na kumwita Mungu. Kuomboleza, <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108456\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">kufunga</span> na <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108227\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">kuomba</span> zilikuwa njia za kuonyesha kuwa watu waligeuka kutoka kwa <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108195\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">dhambi</span>. Vitendo hivi vilionyesha kuwa watu <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108346\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">walitubu</span> dhambi na kumrudia Mungu.</p>",
